license: MIT
keywords:
  - quantum machine learning
  - variational quantum circuits
  - transfer learning
  - plant disease
  - pennylane
  - pytorch
  - plantvillage
abstract: >-
  Code, notebooks, and validation-metric tables for an empirical study of
  hybrid quantum-classical transfer learning (frozen ResNet18 + PennyLane VQC
  head) on PlantVillage-derived leaf-image subsets, with classical baselines
  and multi-seed results on four-class and ten-class tomato classification
  (10 and 16 qubits), including a multi-seed circuit-depth ablation.
